scene.message:
Yukino: A blatantly suspicious{nl}
room. Just two chests in{nl}
the back.{waitkey}{clearbox}It's surely a trap, just like{nl}
the candle room.{waitkey}{clearbox}Best let sleeping dogs lie.{nl}
Let's not touch them.{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: Aww, mean, mean!{nl}
Yuriko went to the trouble{nl}
of preparing a present for{waitkey}you hardworking folks!{waitkey}{clearbox}And you're just gonna ignore{nl}
it and leave? No, no!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hmph. How transparent.{nl}
It's a trap, no doubt.{nl}
Mayuzumi, don't humor her.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: A p-present?{nl}
Y-Yukino, let's take it!{waitkey}{clearbox}They've said it since old{nl}
times - "no villain is fair{nl}
of face"! Let's trust Yuriko!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hmm, it's trap-ish,{nl}
but it looks fun.{waitkey}{clearbox}Running away here would{nl}
feel kinda lame...{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll at least hear her out!{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: Yippee! As expected{nl}
of the girl I get along with{nl}
best - you get it!{waitkey}{clearbox}Yuriko's so happy!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Enough prattle.{nl}
State your business.{nl}
Your way of talking grates.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: It's surely not a proper{nl}
Gift anyway, right?{nl}
Hearing you out is a waste.{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: Geez! Nothing but{nl}
stubborn people! You're happy{nl}
and you know it!{waitkey}{clearbox}Well, fine. Here comes the{nl}
preeeesent explanation!{nl}
Listen up!{waitkey}{clearbox}In one of these two chests,{waitkey}{clearbox}everyone's beloved "Mirror{nl}
Shard" is iiinside!{waitkey}{clearbox}And Yuriko-chan, being{nl}
generous, gives you a chance{nl}
to get it for free!{waitkey}{clearbox}Buut! The chance is only{nl}
ooone! Open the wrong chest{nl}
and there's a penalty!{waitkey}{clearbox}Well? Well? Isn't it fun?{nl}
Do your best!{nl}
Ahahahaha!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: So it's a trap after{nl}
all? But it's a chance!{nl}
C'mon, let's just try it,{waitkey}everyone!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ayase kinda feels like that{nl}
girl isn't lying, at least.{waitkey}{clearbox}Nothing to lose! Ayase'll{nl}
take responsibility!{nl}
Let's open it!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: That Yuriko woman!{nl}
She's toying with our lives{nl}
in the palm of her hand!!{waitkey}{clearbox}What an unpleasant woman,{nl}
honestly.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: I wonder why? That{nl}
Yuriko girl seems like she's{nl}
forcing herself really hard.{waitkey}Ayase gets that feeling.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Kiii! That Yuriko{nl}
girl's a super coward!{nl}
Ayase's super ticked off!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: There are two kinds{nl}
of traps. One is meant to{nl}
kill the target for certain.{waitkey}{clearbox}The other is meant only to{nl}
toy with the target and{nl}
slowly{waitkey}instill terror.{waitkey}{clearbox}Yuriko's trap is surely{nl}
the latter.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Honestly, this tower's{nl}
traps are nasty and no good!{waitkey}{clearbox}For an honest guy like me,{nl}
it's full of danger!{nl}
No, really, seriously.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: To that Yuriko, this{nl}
tower's Traps are a Game.{waitkey}{clearbox}Each time we advance, she{nl}
hurts us just shy of death,{nl}
sometimes even preparing{waitkey}a Gift, you see.{waitkey}{clearbox}That way, Yuriko means to{nl}
Genocide us at the Last of{nl}
her own Game.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Kyaaa?!{nl}
S-something's draining{nl}
from my body{waitkey}{clearbox}it's going away!{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: Ahahahaha!{nl}
Toooo bad!{waitkey}{clearbox}So, as a penalty, I'll take{nl}
another one of you!{waitkey}{clearbox}Buh-byeee!{nl}
Bye-bye!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Kiiii!{nl}
What the, what the!{nl}
Super coward!{waitkey}{clearbox}So frustrating! Ayase{nl}
can't use her Persona{nl}
anymore! What do I do!?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Yay! Bingo!!{nl}
Jackpot!{waitkey}{clearbox}See, see? Just like Ayase{nl}
said, opening the box first{nl}
was the right call, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: Hmm, seems you've got{nl}
pretty good bad luck at least!{nl}
OK! You win this game!{waitkey}Congrats!{waitkey}{clearbox}My room's just a little{nl}
further now, so do your best!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll present you with a truly{nl}
lovely "death." So, I'll be{nl}
waiting!{waitkey}{ret}

Ufufufu... Too bad. Time's{nl}
up...{waitkey}{clearbox}Your desperate struggling was{nl}
the perfect entertainment to{nl}
make the "Eternal Night"{waitkey}all the more splendid.{waitkey}{clearbox}But the opening act ends here.{waitkey}{clearbox}Now, the climax called the{nl}
"Eternal Night"{nl}
raises its curtain.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: H...{wait_fr:30}hey, hey!{nl}
What's started happening?!{nl}
Don't tell me, Yuriko!{waitkey}{clearbox}Did she cut the tower's time{nl}
limit short as a "penalty"?{waitkey}{clearbox}What do we do, Ayase!!{nl}
You... when you opened that{nl}
chest, you said it!!{waitkey}"I'll take responsibility"!{waitkey}{clearbox}What now! That's why I said{nl}
"better not touch it"!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ehh? Ayase?{wait_fr:30} Ayase's{nl}
fault? No way?? Hold on!{waitkey}{clearbox}No way...{wait_fr:30} Ayase didn't think{nl}
it'd turn into such{nl}
a big deal...{waitkey}{clearbox}Ehehe... I said "I'll take{nl}
responsibility" in the heat{nl}
of the moment, but...{waitkey}{clearbox}truth is, Ayase wasn't{nl}
thinking anything at all...{waitkey}{clearbox}It's Yuriko who's bad...{nl}
Ayase's not bad...{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: ...kyaha...{nl}
kyahahahaha{nl}
kyaaahahahahaha...{waitkey}{clearbox}Tiiime uuup!{nl}
Game oooveeer!{nl}
...or so I'd say!{waitkey}{clearbox}Well?{wait_fr:30} Well?{nl}
Surprised, huh??{waitkey}{clearbox}Yuriko-chan's "Snow Queen"{nl}
impression is Academy Award{nl}
material, right?{waitkey}Kyahahahaha!{waitkey}{clearbox}Gotcha!{wait_fr:30} Gotchaaa!{nl}
It was a joooke!{nl}
Ahh! Sooo fun!!{waitkey}{clearbox}You thought it was all over,{nl}
didn't you?{waitkey}{clearbox}Too baaad!! The "Mirror Shard"{nl}
isn't in this box{wait_fr:30}, nope!{waitkey}{clearbox}Buh-byeee!{nl}
Bye-byeee!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ayase's, like, super{nl}
frustrated!! Ahh, geez!!{nl}
Feels like I got super{nl}
tricked?!{waitkey}{clearbox}{ctl0f:1}!! Why didn't you open{nl}
the left box?! Take{nl}
responsibility!{waitkey}{clearbox}It's your fault, you know!{nl}
Ayase's not at fault!{waitkey}{ret}
